# BCD Code Style Guide and Conventions

* Use a beautify package e.g. for Atom https://github.com/Glavin001/atom-beautify and/or Prettier e.g. https://atom.io/packages/prettier-atom
* use uppercase variable names for all const decalrations.
## File Naming
* All javascript files' names should use lowercase seperated by hyphens



## Code comments
* Adopt  [Comment Showing Intent](https://standards.mousepawmedia.com/csi.html)
